thread.title: Elaine

author: Elaine
title: Elaine
text: Recently purchased our first brand new vehicle from Motorama Mitsubishi Springwood, we were looked after by Shanen who was honest and up front with our questions. He provided all the information we needed and was not too pushy giving us the space and time to come to our decision. Very happy with our shiny new Mitsubishi ASX, it has all the bells and whistles with a sporty look and very reasonably priced with great warranty and capped price servicing. After one week of ownership we are very happy.
